        Apply through your volunteer coordinator or local admin to receive a verified glassmorphic digital membership card, equipped with a secure QR verification payload.
      </p>
      <div class="pt-2">
        <a
          href="/verify"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#D4AF37] text-gray-900 font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-amber-400 hover:text-black transition-all shadow-lg active:scale-95"
        >
          <span>🔍</span>
          <span data-ta="உறுப்பினர் அட்டை சரிபார்" data-en="Verify Membership Card">Verify Membership Card</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
